{"tid":1095222,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜公路Chok甫　森美滄桑味似足王傑？ (◔_◔)","createTime":"2019-04-07T00:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T04:06:49.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1cc8cbab11e8cbef5547d01d1fdd01ea3c534d","tid":1095222,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T00:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190407/photo/bkn-20190407083235484-0407_00862_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190407%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190407083235484-0407_00862_001_01p.jpg&h=c25318bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n森美出名型到出汁兼轉數快，不過今次就老貓燒鬆&hellip;佢喺社交網上載咗兩張相，見佢企喺條漆黑嘅既公路上，隔離有部好型嘅電單車，但佢就顯得一臉無奈。雖然佢着晒戰衣，但又好似得物無所用，相信應該係電單車死火等緊救援。佢感慨發文：「事出必有因，為何在西貢山邊。我要這樣滄桑？可以笑的話不會哭，可以飛馳的時候不會像一碌木。」有網友指佢喺公路上呢個甫士與王傑相似，滄桑味出晒嚟！&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔記得王傑有幾滄桑 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /> ？g嬸回帶&darr;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TqNOJGL8mFY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTqNOJGL8mFY&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=a7397847\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TqNOJGL8mFY</a>"},{"pid":"01c9e7fed25dedf85075bdc90d928d78e530a464","tid":1095222,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"可以愛的話不退縮🙄"},{"pid":"18c36f19950efff3a26c96980540bbd5b8d7a04c","tid":1095222,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T01:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以愛的話不退縮🙄</blockquote><br />\n咁佢似唔似一碌木？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbn